Branch: REL_12_STABLE [507b72bd9] 2024-09-17 19:54:26 -0700
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [b8df69049] 2024-11-08 13:42:10 -0500
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [943b65358] 2024-11-08 13:42:01 -0500
